OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with some good
OL,6,Fspells of sunshine. Cloud will tend to
OL,7,Fincrease throughout the day, with a
OL,8,Ffew showers developing across northern
OL,9,Fcounties by the afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining rather cloudy, with
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain during the
OL,14,Fevening. However it will turn drier
OL,15,Fwith clear spells developing later in
OL,16,Fthe night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
