OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, there
OL,6,Fwill be plenty of dry and bright
OL,7,Fweather around on Sunday. Light winds
OL,8,Fand temperatures below average for
OL,9,Fearly to mid-May.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FUnsettled and cool next week, with
OL,13,Frain or showers affecting much of the
OL,14,Fcountry. Some spells of sunshine in
OL,15,Fthe mix too, but feeling chilly, with
OL,16,Fa risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
